      "A firearm mod for version 1.12.2 is a great addition to the Minecraft game, allowing you to use various types of firearms in your adventures. This mod adds new combat possibilities and allows you to fight enemies using powerful firearms.",
    "1122_oruzhie_p_7":
      "If you want to expand your arsenal of weapons in Minecraft 1.12.2, firearm mods will provide you with this opportunity. Here are some popular firearm mods for version 1.12.2:",
    "1122_oruzhie_li_3":
      "Modern Warfare - this mod adds a wide range of modern firearms, such as assault rifles, sniper rifles, pistols, and grenade launchers. You will be able to use these weapon systems to fight enemies and protect your territories.",
    "1122_oruzhie_li_4":
      "Flan's Mod - this is one of the most popular firearm mods, adding a huge amount of diverse weapons, including historical, modern, and futuristic variants. You will be able to collect, customize, and use different types of firearms.",
    "1122_oruzhie_p_8":
      "To download a firearm mod for Minecraft 1.12.2, you should refer to the official resources specializing in Minecraft modifications. There, you will find detailed instructions for installation and usage of the mod.",
    "1122_oruzhie_p_9":
      "Remember that using firearms in the game can change the balance and realism of gameplay. Be careful when using such mods and consider the features of your gameplay and style of play.",
